Responsibilities : 
SAP Functional Knowledge - 
Responsible for SAP Application Maintenance and Support project activities having expertise in SAP Sales and Distribution Module. Expertise in Pricing, Text Determination, Output Determination, Intercompany Sales, STO processes, Third Party sales, Rebates, Consignment Processing and Order Management.
 This role uses consulting skills, business knowledge, and SAP solution expertise to effectively integrate SAP technology into the client?s business environment in order to achieve client expected business results. 
Knowledge in ABAP debugging is a must. 
IT/SAP experience with deep knowledge in SAP Sales and Distribution in client domain. Must have full lifecycle SAP SD implementation experience (Project Preparation till Go-Live). Must have at least 1 production support experience of global similar size client.
 Experience and knowledge in other integration modules. Knowledge on Interfaces. Ability to analyze problems and provide clear recommendations. Strong organizational skills. Able to collaborate with clients and have a strong desire to excel. Excellent communication skills, written and verbal. Good interpersonal skills. Must be able to work independently as well as a team player and can manage own workload. Able to Multi-task and work under tight deadlines.
 Must be an effective problem solver. Experience writing functional/technical specifications. 
Responsibilities : 
Facilitates the support of SAP SD module, Production break fix issues and maintenance/enhancement changes to ensure stable production environment and enhance the clients? business functionality and overall performance, while maintaining a high degree of customer satisfaction.
 Trouble shooting SAP SD processes related system/process/user issues related to Design, configuration and Master and Transaction data and WRICEF objects, Design, configuration and testing, documentation, training of relevant processes.
 Maintains a thorough knowledge of the organization and adheres to all client and organizational standards. Coordinate with Client stakeholders for day to day work stream operation activities and prioritize the work load as required. Create daily and weekly operation status reports.
 Review and ensure the quality of work stream deliverable including the documentation, Change process compliance .etc. Coordinate with cross work stream and client teams as required. 
